dAgency.23 EMS Agency Time Zone No No The time zone for the EMS Agency. D01_19 Optional Associated with each of the EMS Agency Number (dAgency.02). If more than one Time Zone is located within the EMS Agency service area, please chose the time zone covering the greatest volume of EMS events.
